metadata.name: A Powerful Thought
metadata.description:
I encourage everyone to learn how the human brain works. 

Why?

Once you understand how it works, you’ll undoubtedly understand how powerful it is.

Then one day you’ll realize that you’ve been in possession of one of the rarest objects in the universe.

You already have power.

You’ve had it for your entire life: the most powerful tool in the known universe.

Continue to use it well, and you’ll realize that you can have anything you really want in life.

Why?

You already have the only tool you need to get it. 

You just have to remind yourself
